rComments: Probably the teacher I liked the most in my 3 years of uni in Criminology. I've had her 2 times and loved her. She explains so well so it's really easy to understand. She's not there to make you fail. Quizzed and papers are really easy if you do your readings and take good notes.

There are quiz every weeks about the lecture, which could help to understand the material of the class. She is really aware of her student and try to give the must helpful explanation of each theory she's talking about. Really openminded person. Accessible for any comments from her student to give the better of her.

She gives lots of reading to do but they are all related the to material she is using in class or during her exams. The question she write for the exam could be difficult to understand but when you do understand her question properly it is easy to get a great mark. Take home exam is a group projects which is a bit annoying.

As an online class, she's only using a third of the hours she got for the theory which gives us time to do the readings and the quiz inside the class hours every weeks. She is available to answer to any kind of question and does care a lot about her student. Not my first class with her and not the last one either hopefully.

J'ai beaucoup apprécié Mme Strimelle. Elle connait très bien sa matière et est en mesure de répondre aux questions qui ne sont pas tant en rapport avec le cours. Elle a beaucoup d'expérience ce qui rend ses cours agréables. Elle est très drôle et amicale. Une des meilleures profs que j'ai eu! Je reprendrai des cours avec elle à coups sur.
Her lectures are very scattered and she is hard to follow and understand. She is not specific on what she wants from you for tests. She makes a lot of odd jokes and growls at her students.
Mme. Strimelle est excellente comme professeur! Sont enseignement est très stimulant et ses travaux reflètent bien son cours. Je recommande prendre un de ces cours :)

Vraiment une bonne professeure. Explique très clairement, et sa matière est très intéressante et contemporaine.  Je la recommande très fortement.  Elle est de plus très sympathique de façons générale & très accessible comme enseignante.
Claire dans son enseignement- présentations Power Point pourraient être beaucoup plus claires... En général, le cours est excellent.
Excellent professeur, elle explique très bien les concepts et il n'y a pas du de surprise à l'examen.
Tres bonne prof, interessante et je la recommande pour les cours de Crimino..

seems easy at first, but the tests are all multiple choice and don't leave much room for interpretation. Very nice professor, but the class does get a little boring since she just reads off her presentations.
